Enhance participant engagement and provide a seamless application process for participants who cleared the prescreening eligibility. You can configure the built-in Omnistudio components to capture essential participant details, which allows for direct and self-paced application without intermediaries.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Life Sciences Cloud and Participant Enrollment Add-On license.

When: Participant Management is available starting in June 2024.

Who: This feature is available to users with the Health Cloud Starter, OmniStudio Admin and OmniStudio User permission set licenses.

How: From App Launcher, find and select authorization form text to create records. Next, set up person accounts. Create a new version of the built-in candidate registration Omniscript, and add the authorization form text ID and person account record ID to the Omniscript. Then, set up reCAPTCHA. From Setup, go to web-to-case-HTML-Generator, and enter the API key pair you got when registering the site. Add the reCAPTCHA details to the Omniscript and experience cloud site.
title: Simplify Application Process with Built-in Templates in Life Sciences Cloud
